Guide Documentation uses jekyll, minima theme and gulp.

* jekyll: used to build static site in _site folder
* gulp: sync browser and live preview changes.

installation:

install ruby-dev npm

* sudo gem install bundle
* cd guide/
* bundle
* npm install

* gulp -> start webserver + synced browser
* jekyll build -> deploy to _site
* jekyll serve --watch -> deploy to _site and start webserver
